# 1. Ignore EVERYTHING by default
*

# 2. Keep directories (to preserve structure)
!*/

# 3. Whitelist specific source extensions
!*.cpp
!*.hpp
!*.py

# 4. Keep the .gitignore file itself
!.gitignore

# (Optional) If you have build scripts, you might want to uncomment these:
# !Makefile
# !CMakeLists.txt
!README.md
